data.description:
Original Charm and Character! This charming 2 bedroom, 1.5 bath home is located in a desirable neighborhood in the heart of Tulsa, OK. It was built in 1942 and features original hardwood floors, a cozy fireplace, a spacious backyard with mature trees in the front, glass door knobs, and an original bath design.  A great opportunity for a buyer who wants to put their own personal touch on a classic home. Close to schools, shopping, and restaurants.
Schedule a showing today to see all that this charming home has to offer!

To help visualize this home’s floorplan and to highlight its potential, virtual furnishings may have been added to photos found in this listing.
